						               													<description>A muffle fart cool memo game:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Cheesy stinker sock, it smells quite rotten in Schmuddelfing! The Olchis have until 12 noon to free the small town from the bad smell. Then begins the citizens' meeting, at which the future of the dirty finger dump, the home of the Olchis, is decided.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Go together with the Olchi children in search of fine herringbones, toady slippers and crisp batteries. You have to roll in order and reveal cards. As soon as three cards of the same waste are revealed it is automatically selected. But be careful not to accidentally get a voucher for the wellness hotel. Because then it's time to Yikes, off to the bathtub, take a bubble bath, and that costs valuable time!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game starts with an area of 4 times 6 hidden tiles with the player token in one corner and the vouchers in the others.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Roll a dice and either increase the time if the dice shows a clock or move depending on the result 1-3 fields with a single player token. Ensure that the final field is revealed and add a chip on all three tiles with player tokens if they are equal. For the next turn hide the tiles without chip again if you leave it and the next player tries again.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You win the game if the clock shows less than 12 o&amp;lsquo;clock and there are chips on all waste tiles otherwise you loose.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
